<i>I should prepare myself for the worst!</i></b></font>

50
00:04:15,834 --> 00:04:18,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, I got my license.</b></font>

51
00:04:18,934 --> 00:04:23,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, you did? What, automatic only?</b></font>

52
00:04:23,774 --> 00:04:29,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, manual. I can even drive
