59
00:04:48,864 --> 00:04:51,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One day soon, I'm gonna go up against Iketani!</b></font>

60
00:04:51,964 --> 00:04:55,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, so you're a real racer now.</b></font>

61
00:04:55,804 --> 00:05:01,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I guess! If you like,
I'll take you for a drive sometime!</b></font>

62
00:05:20,664 --> 00:05:23,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think? Seems like
a pretty even match, huh?</b></font>

63
00:05:23,904 --> 00:05:27,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as if you can go opening
it full throttle in this rain.</b></font>

64
00:05:27,174 --> 00:05:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The lower the speed range,
the more the FD loses its advantage.</b></font>

65
00:05:43,084 --> 00:05:46,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah. Thank you.</b></font>

66
00:05:46,624 --> 00:05:51,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're just before the road cut hairpins.
It looks like it's a dead heat.</b></font>

67
00:05:51,524 --> 00:05:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not just gonna let us win. That FD is fast.</b></font>

68
00:05:56,064 --> 00:06:02,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At any rate, keeping up with Wataru's
Levin in this rain is no easy task.</b></font>

69
00:06:02,634 --> 00:06:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I thought during the race with Kyoko,
