73
00:06:27,634 --> 00:06:29,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why would you use that in a race?!</b></font>

74
00:06:29,334 --> 00:06:31,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell's with Itsuki?</b></font>

75
00:06:31,164 --> 00:06:35,004
