76
00:06:35,004 --> 00:06:37,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do something, Takumi!</b></font>

77
00:06:37,604 --> 00:06:40,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, well, there's not much I can...</b></font>

78
00:06:40,514 --> 00:06:45,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just look at those leering faces!
What are those two talking about?!</b></font>

79
00:06:45,144 --> 00:06:51,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't know Wataru would be
here until I'd arrived, either.</b></font>

80
00:06:51,154 --> 00:06:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's more, Kazumi showing up
when Itsuki of all guys has to be here...</b></font>

81
00:06:56,154 --> 00:06:59,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure is a coincidence, huh?</b></font>

82
00:06:59,094 --> 00:07:01,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like a soap opera or something!</b></font>

83
00:07:01,464 --> 00:07:07,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If only Itsuki gets a happy ending,</i>
<i>I won't have a leg to stand on!</i></b></font>

84
00:07:07,274 --> 00:07:11,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! Come on Mako, show up!</i></b></font>

85
00:07:11,474 --> 00:07:14,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No chance of that happening...</i></b></font>

86
00:07:22,514 --> 00:07:26,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I'd like to
talk to you about. You mind?</b></font>

87
00:07:31,464 --> 00:07:36,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's done a good job of keeping up.</i>
<i>I should know, having originally had a turbo.</i></b></font>

88
00:07:36,464 --> 00:07:39,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Driving a high-powered turbo</i>
<i>on wet roads is hard!</i></b></font>

89
00:07:39,534 --> 00:07:42,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He may be my enemy,</i>
<i>but that bastard's got great skill.</i></b></font>

90
00:07:45,904 --> 00:07:50,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's just one thing I want to ask.</b></font>

91
00:07:50,214 --> 00:07:53,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it about what happened
just before the goal?</b></font>

92
00:07:53,484 --> 00:08:01,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not that. See, I'm a Ferrari driver.
We're not good at playing chase, like...</b></font>

93
00:08:01,524 --> 00:08:04,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The whole tactical thing,
passing and being passed...</b></font>

94
00:08:04,564 --> 00:08:06,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really not interested in that.</b></font>

95
00:08:06,994 --> 00:08:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I want to know is, simply, where does
your strong sense of motivation come from?</b></font>

96
00:08:22,344 --> 00:08:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt it clearly in the middle of our race.</b></font>

97
00:08:26,244 --> 00:08:29,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've got really strong emotions.</b></font>

98
00:08:29,754 --> 00:08:33,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At the very least, when it comes to car
performance, mine should have an advantage.</b></font>

99
00:08:33,784 --> 00:08:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I don't think there's that much
difference in our driving techniques...</b></font>

100
00:08:49,374 --> 00:08:51,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's strange.</b></font>

101
00:08:51,374 --> 00:08:55,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even though I'm saying this,
you just seem like a regular guy.</b></font>

102
00:08:55,444 --> 00:08:58,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that intense motivation of yours
even shrugs off rain like it's nothing...</b></font>

103
00:08:58,884 --> 00:09:01,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just where does it come from?</b></font>

104
00:09:13,224 --> 00:09:16,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyone who says he's not afraid
of the rain is a rank amateur.</b></font>

105
00:09:16,664 --> 00:09:21,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Driving in the rain wears away at your nerves.</b></font>

106
00:09:21,474 --> 00:09:25,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sustaining your concentration
for a long period of time</b></font>

107
00:09:25,404 --> 00:09:32,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>takes extraordinary willpower and stamina.
I think that's what motivation is.</b></font>

108
00:09:32,084 --> 00:09:35,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I meant when I said
you've got strong emotions.</b></font>

109
00:09:38,524 --> 00:09:40,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Talking from my own experience,</b></font>

110
00:09:40,454 --> 00:09:45,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that degree of emotional strength isn't
possible without a strong sense of purpose.</b></font>

111
00:09:45,694 --> 00:09:48,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your driving is sort of like a pro's.</b></font>

112
00:09:48,294 --> 00:09:51,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like a pro's? It is?</b></font>

113
00:09:58,544 --> 00:10:01,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Beginning the second round!</b></font>

114
00:10:01,044 --> 00:10:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Starting in five seconds!</b></font>

115
00:10:02,814 --> 00:10:04,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four... Three...</b></font>

116
00:10:04,984 --> 00:10:06,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Two... One...
--The second round, let's do this!</b></font>

117
00:10:06,684 --> 00:10:08,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah!
--Go!</b></font>

118
00:10:16,524 --> 00:10:19,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm a bit apprehensive about the second race.</b></font>

119
00:10:19,664 --> 00:10:22,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, he's up against that FD.</b></font>

120
00:10:22,534 --> 00:10:24,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think Wataru will be all right?</b></font>

121
00:10:24,664 --> 00:10:27,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll stick with him, no matter what.</b></font>

122
00:10:27,534 --> 00:10:32,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The roads in this area are like his home course.</b></font>

123
00:10:55,234 --> 00:11:01,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This guy's good. This rain can't be very</i>
<i>pleasant for a high-powered rotary turbo.</i></b></font>

124
00:11:01,234 --> 00:11:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>On wet roads, having as much power as an FD</i></b></font>

125
00:11:03,834 --> 00:11:05,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>means not being able to accelerate normally.</i></b></font>

126
00:11:05,774 --> 00:11:08,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It takes ultra-precise half-throttle acceleration.</i></b></font>

127
00:11:08,674 --> 00:11:13,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But there are no faults in my strategy!</i></b></font>

128
00:11:13,184 --> 00:11:14,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If this becomes a war of attrition,</i></b></font>

129
00:11:14,614 --> 00:11:17,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the car that's harder to control</i>
<i>will cause its driver to slip up.</i></b></font>

130
00:11:17,384 --> 00:11:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Once your concentration is broken,</i>
<i>that's when you make mistakes...</i></b></font>

131
00:11:20,554 --> 00:11:22,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's what will decide this race!</i></b></font>

132
00:11:25,524 --> 00:11:29,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You say that, but I still don't really understand.</b></font>

133
00:11:29,734 --> 00:11:33,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I always feel that I want to get better.</b></font>

134
00:11:33,264 --> 00:11:38,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think the other members of Project D
are much more "like a pro" than me.</b></font>

135
00:11:38,874 --> 00:11:44,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, I just race as hard as I can
and try not to drag them down.</b></font>

136
00:11:44,444 --> 00:11:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so? Then it's probably your environment.</b></font>

137
00:11:49,714 --> 00:11:51,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How old are you?</b></font>

138
00:11:51,384 --> 00:11:52,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nineteen.</b></font>

139
00:11:52,724 --> 00:11:57,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nineteen?! I'll be 26 this year.</b></font>

140
00:11:57,124 --> 00:12:05,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I'd had your technique when I was 19,
I think my life would've been a lot different.</b></font>

141
00:12:05,934 --> 00:12:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm jealous of you.</b></font>

142
00:12:08,274 --> 00:12:10,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I'd just put in the extra effort,</b></font>

143
00:12:10,674 --> 00:12:14,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd be in an environment where
I could race as fast as I like.</b></font>

144
00:12:14,074 --> 00:12:17,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been in something of a slump recently...</b></font>

145
00:12:17,614 --> 00:12:23,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanted to ask you in case I could
pick up any hints. Sorry to bother you.</b></font>

146
00:12:28,754 --> 00:12:34,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Motivation, huh? I've come this far</i>
<i>without really giving it much thought.</i></b></font>

147
00:12:34,764 --> 00:12:38,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just being in Project D</i>
<i>gets me naturally motivated.</i></b></font>

148
00:12:38,504 --> 00:12:42,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I think I've found myself in an</i>
<i>incredibly blessed environment.</i></b></font>

149
00:12:45,704 --> 00:12:50,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Also, I love this car!</i></b></font>

150
00:12:50,014 --> 00:12:56,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So... my strongest emotion is not wanting</i>
<i>to lose to Keisuke, my own teammate!</i></b></font>

151
00:13:16,074 --> 00:13:18,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's keeping up with me after all, eh?</i></b></font>

152
00:13:22,144 --> 00:13:24,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's to be expected.</i></b></font>

153
00:13:24,044 --> 00:13:29,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With MUs this low, I can only</i>
<i>run my engine at half strength.</i></b></font>

154
00:13:31,054 --> 00:13:35,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My FD isn't in its element</i>
<i>unless it's in a high-speed race.</i></b></font>

155
00:13:37,594 --> 00:13:40,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The old me probably would've blown his top,</i></b></font>

156
00:13:40,224 --> 00:13:44,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but that accelerator training I've been</i>
<i>doing recently is coming in handy.</i></b></font>

157
00:13:44,504 --> 00:13:47,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Anyway, I have to wait it out.</i>
<i>My chance will definitely come!</i></b></font>

158
00:13:47,674 --> 00:13:51,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If he could win, then I can definitely win, too!</i></b></font>

159
00:13:57,274 --> 00:13:59,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This race has gotten deadlocked, huh?</b></font>

160
00:13:59,384 --> 00:14:02,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Having to draw it out longer
works against Keisuke.</b></font>

161
00:14:02,854 --> 00:14:07,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In these rainy conditions, he should have
no anxiety regarding the car's mechanics...</b></font>

162
00:14:07,454 --> 00:14:11,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So all the pressure falls onto the driver, huh?</b></font>

163
00:14:11,024 --> 00:14:15,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's his nerves that get worn down.</b></font>

164
00:14:15,064 --> 00:14:17,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder how long Keisuke
can sustain his concentration.</b></font>

165
00:14:17,804 --> 00:14:20,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem like you enjoy it. Tormenting Keisuke.</b></font>

166
00:14:20,634 --> 00:14:22,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not it.</b></font>

167
00:14:22,134 --> 00:14:24,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll never get a better chance than this</b></font>

168
00:14:24,274 --> 00:14:28,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to fully master the task he's been undertaking.</b></font>

169
00:14:28,214 --> 00:14:30,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll have him race long and leisurely.</b></font>

170
00:14:30,474 --> 00:14:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, you've got a point...</b></font>

171
00:14:33,214 --> 00:14:37,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Techniques that do not come alive during
actual, pressure-filled races are meaningless.</b></font>

172
00:14:37,554 --> 00:14:41,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Meaning Keisuke's got it tough, as usual.</b></font>

173
00:14:49,334 --> 00:14:51,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That bastard's still right on my tail.</i></b></font>

174
00:14:52,834 --> 00:14:56,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A supercharger, huh? That was clever.</i></b></font>

175
00:14:56,134 --> 00:14:59,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even though we have the same setup that</i>
<i>uses air pressure to drive our turbines,</i></b></font>

176
00:14:59,444 --> 00:15:04,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>his also gets power supplied</i>
<i>directly from the crankshaft.</i></b></font>

177
00:15:04,514 --> 00:15:11,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My system's greatest merit is that it gets power</i>
<i>directly proportional to increased RPMs.</i></b></font>

178
00:15:11,584 --> 00:15:17,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With a turbocharger there's a differential,</i>
<i>or turbo lag, but not with this setup.</i></b></font>

179
00:15:17,254 --> 00:15:20,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even though a turbo gives you</i>
<i>more of an increase in power,</i></b></font>

180
00:15:20,694 --> 00:15:26,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>with this, you just step on the gas to get</i>
<i>regulated power, regardless of conditions!</i></b></font>

181
00:15:28,104 --> 00:15:31,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If you're out on winding roads</i>
<i>with low average speed,</i></b></font>

182
00:15:31,944 --> 00:15:36,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>a supercharger will definitely give you</i>
<i>more fighting advantage than a turbo!</i></b></font>

183
00:15:54,394 --> 00:15:58,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible! They're going out
for a third race, huh?</b></font>

184
00:15:58,234 --> 00:16:01,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Neither of them can seem to clinch it.</b></font>

185
00:16:01,204 --> 00:16:04,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess that means their
skills are evenly matched.</b></font>

186
00:16:04,404 --> 00:16:06,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's because of the rain.</b></font>

187
00:16:06,544 --> 00:16:11,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Starting in five seconds! Four! Three! Two!
--It makes the rear car keep pace with the lead.</b></font>

188
00:16:11,544 --> 00:16:15,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--One! Go!
--If they raced separately you'd
see a difference in their times,</b></font>

189
00:16:15,484 --> 00:16:20,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but with these rules, sometimes the cars
just pull each other along like magnets.</b></font>

190
00:16:20,324 --> 00:16:23,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet the two of them are tired by now, huh?</b></font>

191
00:16:23,354 --> 00:16:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure they are,
but they're still concentrating.</b></font>

192
00:16:26,664 --> 00:16:29,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you've realized you're tired,</b></font>

193
00:16:29,334 --> 00:16:33,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you've already started to lose your
concentration, and that's dangerous.</b></font>

194
00:16:33,264 --> 00:16:37,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's why the moment that decides
the race is disappointingly short.</b></font>

195
00:16:44,174 --> 00:16:46,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! I'm not gonna lose!</i></b></font>

196
00:16:46,544 --> 00:16:50,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now that it's come down to this,</i>
<i>it's a battle of motivation!</i></b></font>

197
00:16:50,254 --> 00:16:53,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Some rich kid who doesn't worry</i>
<i>about money wouldn't understand,</i></b></font>

198
00:16:53,084 --> 00:16:56,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but there's a drive and</i>
<i>willpower that money can't buy!</i></b></font>

199
00:16:56,054 --> 00:17:00,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And havin' me win would make</i>
<i>things that much more dramatic!</i></b></font>

200
00:17:06,364 --> 00:17:09,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This has turned into a
pretty incredible race, huh?</b></font>

201
00:17:09,374 --> 00:17:14,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure has. They just keep racing in the
middle of this rain without any breaks.</b></font>

202
00:17:14,274 --> 00:17:17,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think Wataru is totally incredible!</b></font>

203
00:17:17,374 --> 00:17:20,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even on the hillclimb,
he doesn't lose an inch to the FD!</b></font>

204
00:17:20,914 --> 00:17:24,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As someone who drives a
Levin too, I really admire him!</b></font>

205
00:17:24,254 --> 00:17:26,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Admire him? My brother?</b></font>

206
00:17:26,624 --> 00:17:29,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah!
--You shouldn't.</b></font>

207
00:17:29,294 --> 00:17:31,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's so great about him, anyway?</b></font>

208
00:17:31,264 --> 00:17:37,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"What"? Well, everything!
He's cool, he's serious about cars...</b></font>

209
00:17:37,094 --> 00:17:41,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The way he insisted on a Levin instead
of some new car is totally macho!</b></font>

210
00:17:41,474 --> 00:17:44,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's just that he doesn't have any money!</b></font>

211
00:17:47,404 --> 00:17:50,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's got no money, huh? Hey, neither do I!</b></font>

212
00:17:50,174 --> 00:17:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm jealous... They're having a great time!</i></b></font>

213
00:18:02,354 --> 00:18:06,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Levin's movements have</i>
<i>started to become a little weird.</i></b></font>

214
00:18:06,624 --> 00:18:11,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He must be tired, too. Maybe</i>
<i>it's time I try moving into action.</i></b></font>

215
00:18:11,434 --> 00:18:14,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm gonna put as much</i>
<i>pressure on him as I can!</i></b></font>

216
00:18:18,644 --> 00:18:23,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! He's trying to ramp up the</i>
<i>pressure, huh? I'm not falling for it!</i></b></font>

217
00:18:23,474 --> 00:18:25,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't be the only one suffering through this.</i></b></font>

218
00:18:25,844 --> 00:18:28,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's see who can last longer!</i></b></font>

219
00:18:46,904 --> 00:18:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You finally showed up, huh? Hiding in
a corner somewhere doesn't suit you.</b></font>

220
00:18:53,074 --> 00:18:56,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You came to support
Keisuke Takahashi, didn't you?</b></font>

221
00:18:56,244 --> 00:18:57,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, Nobuhiko.</b></font>

222
00:18:57,984 --> 00:19:04,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about that. It's not
as if we're at war or anything.</b></font>

223
00:19:04,184 --> 00:19:07,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Feel free to go ahead and
support whoever you like.</b></font>

224
00:19:17,434 --> 00:19:21,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being in the rain's got him
wobbling around that much, huh?</b></font>

225
00:19:21,704 --> 00:19:25,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>FRs sure are pieces of junk.</b></font>

226
00:19:25,004 --> 00:19:29,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I wanted to beat him,
I could do it any time I wanted.</b></font>

227
00:19:29,174 --> 00:19:32,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not that it would be a fair fight...</b></font>

228
00:19:42,394 --> 00:19:44,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I feel like he's really on my tail.</i></b></font>

229
00:19:44,964 --> 00:19:49,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder why... If it's because I'm tired</i>
<i>and my pace has dropped, that's bad.</i></b></font>

230
00:19:49,534 --> 00:19:51,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've gotta really floor it!</i></b></font>

231
00:20:01,444 --> 00:20:05,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is bad. It's getting to</i>
<i>where I can't control it.</i></b></font>

232
00:20:05,284 --> 00:20:09,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does this mean I've almost</i>
<i>lost my ability to concentrate?</i></b></font>

233
00:20:09,114 --> 00:20:13,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Humans can't sustain intense
concentration for long.</b></font>

234
00:20:13,424 --> 00:20:17,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When pushed to the very limit,
about 30 minutes is the maximum.</b></font>

235
00:20:17,754 --> 00:20:18,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, but...</b></font>

236
00:20:18,994 --> 00:20:24,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pro racers have to keep going
for two to three hours, right?</b></font>

237
00:20:24,094 --> 00:20:29,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may be a race, but it's not
as if they're going at 100%.</b></font>

238
00:20:29,634 --> 00:20:33,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the circuit, there are long
straightaways where one can relax.</b></font>

239
00:20:33,444 --> 00:20:38,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So in that sense, there's no place
to relax on a winding public road.</b></font>

240
00:20:38,784 --> 00:20:41,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the rain, there is little visibility
and the road is slippery.</b></font>

241
00:20:41,454 --> 00:20:43,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't let your guard down for a second.</b></font>

242
00:20:43,414 --> 00:20:47,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What exactly happens when
your concentration is broken?</b></font>

243
00:20:47,024 --> 00:20:49,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>First, your concentration becomes dulled.</b></font>

244
00:20:49,424 --> 00:20:53,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your reflexes slow.
The smallest things cause stress.</b></font>

245
00:20:53,464 --> 00:20:56,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You become unable to do two things at once.</b></font>

246
00:20:56,294 --> 00:20:59,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When the end comes, it is disappointingly fast.</b></font>

247
00:21:03,474 --> 00:21:07,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good luck, my darling. Don't let him beat you!</i></b></font>

248
00:21:07,504 --> 00:21:10,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll always be here for you, darling!</i></b></font>

249
00:21:23,954 --> 00:21:25,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rain's suddenly picked up.</b></font>

250
00:21:25,894 --> 00:21:28,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's really coming down now!</b></font>

251
00:21:54,254 --> 00:21:55,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't see!</i></b></font>

252
00:21:57,224 --> 00:22:01,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There should be a mid-speed section</i>
<i>up ahead that veers sharply to the left.</i></b></font>

253
00:22:39,604 --> 00:22:41,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit!</b></font>

254
00:22:54,544 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You all right?</b></font>

255
00:22:56,154 --> 00:23:01,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I stopped just short of the concrete wall.</b></font>

256
00:23:01,224 --> 00:23:04,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah. You spun out on a good angle there.</b></font>

257
00:23:04,654 --> 00:23:10,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One of my talents. This may
sound like an excuse, but...</b></font>

258
00:23:10,334 --> 00:23:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know where all the gutters on this course are,
and I can tell you how many there are.</b></font>

259
00:23:17,474 --> 00:23:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But for just a second, I got distracted
by the switch for the windshield wiper</b></font>

260
00:23:21,674 --> 00:23:27,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and that gutter spun me right out. All I
can say is, I just wasn't thinking straight.</b></font>

261
00:23:27,644 --> 00:23:30,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even I still can't believe it.</b></font>

262
00:23:30,684 --> 00:23:36,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess that's what it is...
to have your concentration broken.</b></font>

263
00:23:45,134 --> 00:23:49,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru spun out. We lose.</b></font>

264
00:23:52,844 --> 00:23:54,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like Keisuke won!</b></font>

265
00:23:54,174 --> 00:23:57,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'd prepared ourselves
for an all-out victory, but...</b></font>

266
00:23:57,774 --> 00:23:59,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is very disappointing.</b></font>

267
00:23:59,684 --> 00:24:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Indeed. If it weren't for this rain, I'm certain
you would have won the downhill.</b></font>

268
00:24:24,234 --> 00:24:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru...</b></font>

269
00:24:25,704 --> 00:24:27,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Brother...</b></font>

270
00:24:31,984 --> 00:24:34,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost.</b></font>

271
00:24:34,014 --> 00:24:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We were utterly defeated. Project D...</i></b></font>

272
00:24:37,054 --> 00:24:42,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And Ryosuke Takahashi! They're on</i>
<i>a completely different level from us.</i></b></font>

273
00:24:42,694 --> 00:24:46,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, we're moving out!
Be sure to pick up all your trash!</b></font>

274
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A rose that's bloomed on the battlefield,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

275
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A caterpillar that can only move forward</i>
<i>tramples it under foot again today</i></b></font>

276
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, increasing only hatred</i></b></font>

277
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, with those</i>
<i>social conditions transmitted live</i></b></font>

278
00:25:37,474 --> 00:25:46,224
